say what you have on your

00:31:29.040 --> 00:31:32.780
mind with your team members and
other people, and when is

00:31:32.780 --> 00:31:37.800
it appropriate to hold back
your genuine feedback, and

00:31:37.800 --> 00:31:39.870
look for the right time
and right place

00:31:39.870 --> 00:31:41.590
to give that feedback.

00:31:41.590 --> 00:31:44.960
In India, as I grew up, there
