As of last year, Aravind Eye
Care is the largest eye care

00:40:01.860 --> 00:40:06.590
system in the world, operating
at one 10th the

00:40:06.590 --> 00:40:08.540
cost of United Kingdom.

00:40:08.540 --> 00:40:11.800
They provide more services
than the entire

00:40:11.800 --> 00:40:13.660
United Kingdom provides.

