00:40:19.080 --> 00:40:22.330
They got the patent from the
United States, they got the

00:40:22.330 --> 00:40:24.240
license from United States.

00:40:24.240 --> 00:40:27.273
Same cataract lenses
are being sold for

00:40:27.273 --> 00:40:29.490
$150 in United States.

00:40:29.490 --> 00:40:32.760
In India, they offer
it for $2.

00:40:32.760 --> 00:40:36.050
I was told it has come
down to $1 now.

00:40:36.050 --> 00:40:38.760
And for every one paid surgery,

00:40:38.760 --> 00:40:41.410
they do two free surgeries.

