[INAUDIBLE], one of the authors
actually lives in

00:40:47.800 --> 00:40:49.200
[INAUDIBLE].

00:40:49.200 --> 00:40:53.980
So when you have a larger
purpose, when you have a noble

00:40:53.980 --> 00:40:57.740
purpose, your smartness
can actually

00:40:57.740 --> 00:41:00.100
serve a larger community.

00:41:00.100 --> 00:41:03.210
So each of you being
extraordinarily smart, you

00:41:03.210 --> 00:41:07.240
might want to think about and
say, where am I contributing?

00:41:07.240 --> 00:41:09.220
What is my North Star?

00:41:09.220 --> 00:41:11.650
What is my noble purpose?

00:41:11.650 --> 00:41:15.220
Where do I want to be 10 years
from now, 20 years from now?

00:41:15.220 --> 00:41:18.470
It is good to do 10x
contribution at this moment,

00:41:18.470 --> 00:41:22.780
but 10 years from now or 20
years from now, what would you

00:41:22.780 --> 00:41:25.350
like to say to your children--

00:41:25.350 --> 00:41:28.440
and for some of you later than
that-- maybe to your

00:41:28.440 --> 00:41:33.230
grandchildren, what have you
contributed to the planet?

00:41:33.230 --> 00:41:36.400
If you can begin to think
about it, then your

00:41:36.400 --> 00:41:37.610
performance--

00:41:37.610 --> 00:41:39.830
whatever do today, tomorrow--

00:41:39.830 --> 00:41:41.730
it will come with a purpose.

00:41:41.730 --> 00:41:45.120
That is what Indra Nooyi
did in PepsiCo.

00:41:45.120 --> 00:41:50.350
Not only they are looking at
making the drinks, Coca Cola

00:41:50.350 --> 00:41:54.040
drinks, and pizza,
and all of them--

00:41:54.040 --> 00:41:58.120
doing food, what you
call a fun food--

00:41:58.120 --> 00:41:59.080
it's OK.

00:41:59.080 --> 00:42:03.420
They said, we want to get more
profit from good-for-you

00:42:03.420 --> 00:42:07.200
foods, not just fun-for-you
foods.

00:42:07.200 --> 00:42:11.560
Because of that, they've went
ahead and said, we buy Quaker

00:42:11.560 --> 00:42:13.490
Oats for oatmeal.

00:42:13.490 --> 00:42:16.500
We want to create more kinds
of healthy food.

00:42:16.500 --> 00:42:19.690
Of course, their own stock
holders don't like it.

00:42:19.690 --> 00:42:23.040
So she's actually fighting
sometimes for her own

00:42:23.040 --> 00:42:26.950
position, because everybody
wants you to make money right

00:42:26.950 --> 00:42:30.440
now, but they don't care about
anything-- where it goes, and

00:42:30.440 --> 00:42:31.750
how it happens.

00:42:31.750 --> 00:42:35.310
So at some level, you need to
look at it and say, how do you

00:42:35.310 --> 00:42:37.870
reconcile your long-term
vision with

00:42:37.870 --> 00:42:40.230
your short-term delivery?

00:42:40.230 --> 00:42:41.910
That is where the
wisdom comes.

00:42:41.910 --> 00:42:45.260
You cannot just say, I will only
focus on the vision; or

00:42:45.260 --> 00:42:47.950
you cannot just say, I will
only focus on quarterly

00:42:47.950 --> 00:42:50.190
results of what I need to do.

00:42:50.190 --> 00:42:54.010
The wisdom is to be able to
balance both of them, and

00:42:54.010 --> 00:42:56.550
align your head and your
heart and the hands.

00:42:56.550 --> 00:43:00.670
When you bring that alignment,
the wisdom is something that

00:43:00.670 --> 00:43:03.980
actually naturally emerges
in all of it.

