00:46:11.950 --> 00:46:13.270
PRASAD KAIPA: OK, thank you.

00:46:13.270 --> 00:46:15.470
One action orientation.

00:46:15.470 --> 00:46:19.580
Smartness is about thinking,
wisdom is about doing.

00:46:19.580 --> 00:46:21.760
Wisdom is always here and now.

00:46:21.760 --> 00:46:25.760
Smartness is always about the
future you are creating.

00:46:25.760 --> 00:46:30.850
So you need to realize that the
wisdom will not come by

00:46:30.850 --> 00:46:32.570
reading out of a book.

00:46:32.570 --> 00:46:36.100
But if you can-- let us say,
some of you, because you got

00:46:36.100 --> 00:46:38.752
the book as you came in--
let us say you create

00:46:38.752 --> 00:46:40.740
a small book club.

00:46:40.740 --> 00:46:45.840
Start talking about every week,
one chapter, or one part

00:46:45.840 --> 00:46:49.490
of a chapter, and see how you
can apply it in your immediate

00:46:49.490 --> 00:46:53.710
work or in your family
outside.

00:46:53.710 --> 00:46:55.570
Try to share those things.

00:46:55.570 --> 00:46:57.520
You can even create
a Google Hangout.

00:46:57.520 --> 00:47:00.270
You can create some of other
ways of sharing it.

00:47:00.270 --> 00:47:03.600
Begin to apply one
step at a time.

00:47:03.600 --> 00:47:09.120
If you can do that, chances are
90 days from now, you will

00:47:09.120 --> 00:47:10.260
be much wiser.

00:47:10.260 --> 00:47:13.700
But you see, saying that
is much easier.

00:47:13.700 --> 00:47:17.090
I'm sure you have hundred
reasons why you don't have

00:47:17.090 --> 00:47:21.160
time, you don't have enough
people, it takes energy--

00:47:21.160 --> 00:47:23.820
you have too many things on
your plate to be able to

00:47:23.820 --> 00:47:25.900
organize any of this stuff.

00:47:25.900 --> 00:47:30.360
So what it means is, one,
it is cognitive framing.

00:47:30.360 --> 00:47:34.050
Don't look at wisdom as
something away from

00:47:34.050 --> 00:47:35.180
what you are doing.

00:47:35.180 --> 00:47:38.480
As a matter of fact, whatever is
written about in the book,

00:47:38.480 --> 00:47:42.220
or what I'm talking about, is
about application of what

00:47:42.220 --> 00:47:47.150
you're doing in a smarter,
in a wiser way

00:47:47.150 --> 00:47:49.430
right now, right here.

00:47:49.430 --> 00:47:51.470
So wisdom is not just
about long-term.

00:47:51.470 --> 00:47:54.780
So that is one thing
you need let go.

00:47:54.780 --> 00:47:58.370
That means focus
on applying it.

00:47:58.370 --> 00:48:03.400
Second, do it with other people,
because wisdom grows

00:48:03.400 --> 00:48:05.900
when you have multiple
questions, and people

00:48:05.900 --> 00:48:07.200
challenge you.

00:48:07.200 --> 00:48:10.500
It is not about showing off
how smart you are in the

00:48:10.500 --> 00:48:15.040
group, but asking questions so
that all of you can learn.

00:48:15.040 --> 00:48:18.530
Wisdom multiplies
and synergizes.

00:48:18.530 --> 00:48:21.870
So that is something which is
hard for people to look at.

00:48:21.870 --> 00:48:25.280
Third one I found is a barrier,
if several times we

00:48:25.280 --> 00:48:30.030
look at, it is outside of
what I'm supposed to do.

00:48:30.030 --> 00:48:33.790
I will do this, and if I have
time, I will read the book.

00:48:33.790 --> 00:48:37.640
If I have time, I will apply
it, without recognizing

00:48:37.640 --> 00:48:42.750
whatever you have to make
it more executable, more

00:48:42.750 --> 00:48:45.800
successful, you need wisdom.

00:48:45.800 --> 00:48:51.400
Because as you saw Larry doing,
it is not about adding

00:48:51.400 --> 00:48:54.390
more projects that makes
Google successful.

00:48:54.390 --> 00:48:58.450
It is about removing certain
things which are not having a

00:48:58.450 --> 00:49:02.835
high impact, and focusing on a
smaller number of them with

00:49:02.835 --> 00:49:06.990
the discernment, and making them
deeper, more profound,

00:49:06.990 --> 00:49:10.366
more meaningful, and more
higher quality.

00:49:10.366 --> 00:49:13.260
For that, you need
discernment.

00:49:13.260 --> 00:49:17.310
So similarly, if you can begin
to recognize, acting with

00:49:17.310 --> 00:49:20.600
wisdom, you have everything
what it takes.

00:49:20.600 --> 00:49:21.390
You did just that.

00:49:21.390 --> 00:49:23.640
You need to put it
in practice.

00:49:23.640 --> 00:49:27.070
Acting with smartness, you
may need more knowledge.

00:49:27.070 --> 00:49:30.990
You may need to read more, or
you may need to actually talk

00:49:30.990 --> 00:49:33.230
more, or do something else.

00:49:33.230 --> 00:49:36.260
These are three major barriers
I have seen.

00:49:36.260 --> 00:49:40.360
Many smart people, despite
having the resources--

00:49:40.360 --> 00:49:45.130
time, our cognitive framing,
and third, application--

00:49:45.130 --> 00:49:46.590
this are some things which you
need to pay attention.

